    "description": "<!-- MOBILE DESCRIPTION -->\n<div style=\"display:none\">\n<div vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n<span property=\"description\">The ASR Outdoor Sluice Box Gold Prospecting Kit comes with everything you'll need to pan for gold anywhere, anytime!<BR><BR>The backbone of this kit is made up of the ASR Outdoor Backpack Folding Gold Sluice Box for Gold Prospecting features a 3-piece folding design and a 50-inch gravity fed sluice box channel with zinc plated riffle traps creating this high recovery gold prospecting and mineral collection prospecting and gold panning tool. Extremely portable, folding down in size simply by loosening the connecting wing nuts, it will pack right up into your backpack. You're ready to prospect for gold right out of the package with woven vinyl miners moss included and installed.<BR><BR>Simplify your gold prospecting and mining with the ASR Outdoor Aluminum Folding Gold Sluice Box</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- MAIN DESCRIPTION -->\n<html>\n<head>\n\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t/* FONTS AND COLORS */\n\t\tbody {\n\t\t\tfont-family: Arial,sans-serif;\n\t\t\tfont-size: 14px;\n\t\t\tline-height: 1.428571429;\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t\tbackground-color: white;\n\t\t}\n\t\th1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n\t\t\tcolor: black;\n\t\t}\n\t\tp {\n\t\t\twhite-space: pre-line;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.navbar a, .navbar a:active, .navbar a:hover, .navbar a:visited {\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.product-specs {\n\t\t\tbackground-color: #f1f1f1;\n\t\t\tpadding: 1em;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.product-specs td {\n\t\t\tfont-size:12px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-left {\n\t\t\tmin-width:6em;\n\t\t\tfont-weight:bold;\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-right {\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tdiv.footer {\n\t\t\tborder-top: 1px solid #f1f1f1;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.navbar-default {\n\t\t\tbackground-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n\t\t\tbackg